            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-b917a481-f29f-4b10-8388-e0a408c4b41c">
                Mr. Alport  (Colchester)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-b917a481-f29f-4b10-8388-e0a408c4b41c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
