                Mr. George Wigg  (Dudley)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-4ba99c8c-a9d7-4c15-af47-5b9cd8f701f6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
