    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Does the hon. and learned Member consider that bulk selling by the State, as in the case of the sale of cocoa by the Ministry of Food, is equally a monopoly?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-40cb2873-2015-4c1f-832c-a919473f3d92" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
