<p class="">Is it not a fact that the tin market is today a free market and that the fabulous prices which are being demanded for tin are demanded by private sellers?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-84468aba-5c10-44c0-80c6-0ab699ce3b59" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
