            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-4f123f63-9e23-44e6-9e28-c26c25d6d9e6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
