<p class="">If I may continue, possibly the point will be covered. I have promised to be very short and do not want to continue any longer than is necessary.<p></p> Meat is necessary to us in these islands to give us the strength to work and the morale to deal with the problems that lie ahead.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
