<p class="">The hon. and gallant Gentleman is pursuing an interesting line of argument. Perhaps he would indicate what prices he would pay now.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-178dcc24-208b-4137-911f-5b245e3aac8a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
