    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Would the hon. Gentleman explain what he means by helping the Minister to call a halt to inflation in this country? Does he mean that the Government are inflating the economy?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
