            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-3a9f3594-156a-4e1e-9499-ddcf01f83310">
                The Chancellor of the Exchequer (Mr. Gaitskell)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-3a9f3594-156a-4e1e-9499-ddcf01f83310" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-02-08/debates/87ba4790-b102-4735-90e4-d14439a1c3d6/MeatSupplies#contribution-3a9f3594-156a-4e1e-9499-ddcf01f83310">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
