                Mr. Gaitskell
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a9fb051e-63dc-4ca4-aea0-10f6be0c4561" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-02-08/debates/87ba4790-b102-4735-90e4-d14439a1c3d6/MeatSupplies#contribution-a9fb051e-63dc-4ca4-aea0-10f6be0c4561">
