    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Mr. Speaker, can you not keep the Opposition in their place?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1fdef2c9-dbe5-43af-91b7-372bb3278bca" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-02-08/debates/87ba4790-b102-4735-90e4-d14439a1c3d6/MeatSupplies#contribution-1fdef2c9-dbe5-43af-91b7-372bb3278bca">
